1.title: Adding two numbers
1.text: Double click on '+' to add the two numbers

1.title: Multiplying two numbers
1.text: Click on the * sign to multiply

2.title: Swapping terms in expression
2.text: Click and drag 'A' to the far left side

3.title: Swapping terms in expression
3.text: Click and drag 'D' to the far left side

5.title: Commuting fractions
5.text: Click and drag the - next to the T

6.title: Distributing to terms
6.text: Move P on top of '+' to factor

6.title: Simplifying terms inside paranthesis
6.text: Click on the + to simplify inside paranthesis

6.title: Simplifying fractions
6.text: Drag the 8 over 4 to simplify the fraction

7.title: Factoring terms
7.text: Move the first J over the other

8.title: Commuting in longer equations
8.text: Drag C to the left of the equation

9.title: Factoring Fractions
9.text: Drag first M onto the second

9.title: Separating fractions
9.text: Drag B out of the fraction to separate

10.title: Commuting into fractions
10.text: Drag A to the left of D

5.title: Division to multiplication
5.text: Drag 2 to the left hand side

9.title: Combining exponents
9.text: Drag 2 onto the other 2 and continue dragging upwards

10.title: Cancelling same denominators
10.text: Drag the 4 onto the other 4 to cancel them
